休斯顿地下说唱传奇 BeatKing 去世，享年 39 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-after-houston-underground-rap-legend-beatking-dies-age-39-3784551?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tributes-paid-after-休斯顿地下说唱传奇beatking死亡年龄39Max Pilley Fri, 16 Aug 2024 20:45:51 +0000 Music NewsNews..Hip-hopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3784551 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="节拍之王" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，这位颇具影响力的南方说唱明星因肺栓塞去世</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-after-houston-underground-rap-legend-beatking-dies-age-39-3784551">休斯敦地下说唱传奇 BeatKing 去世（享年 39 岁）后发表的悼念</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="节拍之王" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/beatking_rip_rapper-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> BeatKing 是休斯敦说唱音乐界最具影响力的地下人物之一，于 39 岁去世。</p><p> BeatKing 的经理 Tasha Felder 周四晚（8 月 15 日）在 Instagram 上证实了这一消息，她援引了自己的绰号 Club Godzilla，写道：“今天，2024 年 8 月 15 日，我们失去了@Clubgodzilla。”</p><p> “十多年来，BeatKing 一直是俱乐部最好的部分，”她补充道。 “他制作并与如此多的艺术家合作，他的声音将永远存在。他爱他的女儿@clubgodparenting、他的音乐和他的粉丝。我们将永远爱他。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-tf62WNLBz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.3