ckquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tre-cool">Tré Cool</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-dirnt">Mike Dirnt</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-joe-armstrong">Billie Joe Armstrong</a>组成的乐队目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-2024-saviors-stadium-tour-including-huge-london-show-buy-tickets-3529041">正在庆祝他们的两张经典专辑</a>：1994 年的《Dookie》（今年将迎来 30 岁生日）和《American Idiot》（美国白痴）。 20 岁了。在演出中，乐队在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rancid">Rancid</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-linda-lindas">The Linda Lindas</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">The Smashing Pumpkins</a>的支持下完整地演奏了两张唱片。</p><p>在其他地方，乐队最近宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-american-idiot-20th-anniversary-reissue-new-documentary-unreleased-songs-3782343">《American Idiot》的 20 周年纪念版扩大版再版，</a>其中包含一部新纪录片和多首未发行的曲目。</p><p>即将推出的套装包含 15 首未发行的《American Idiot》小样、2004 年在纽约市欧文广场录制的 15 首现场表演、九首此前未发行的现场录音（包括翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a>的《We Are The Champions》）以及14 首歌曲以前仅作为 B 面和奖励曲目提供。</p><p>此外，其中一张蓝光光盘将包含一部全新的 110 分钟纪录片，名为<i>《美国白痴 20 年》</i> 。另一张光盘收录了<i>《Heart Like A Hand Grenade》</i>电影，记录了他们录制《American Idiot》时“与 Green Day 一起度过的九个月”。</p><p>本周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-green-days-new-monsters-saviors-skate-film-3784177">乐队还为一部新的 11 分钟滑板电影《Monsters And Saviors》制作了配乐，</a>由 Russell Houghten 执导。该项目是 Green Day 和 Monster Energy 之间的合作，旨在庆祝一月份发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737">的同名专辑</a>。看看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="滑板电影《怪物与救世主》怪物能源 x @GreenDay" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UaAoa4oh3l8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <i>NME</i>在对 Green Day 6 月份曼彻斯特“Saviors”巡演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/green-day-live-manchester-concert-review-dookie-american-idiot-saviors-tour-setlist-3767978">五星级评论</a>中写道：“随着<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/smashing-pumpkins">The Smashing Pumpkins</a>和 Weezer 在整个月的英国演出，摇滚迷们可以轻描淡写地说：被宠坏了选择。然而，这群人中的最佳选择可能就是绿日乐队的“救世主”巡演：将阶级、青春和邋遢的朋克歌曲结合成一场标志性的体育场摇滚活动。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-green-day-speed-through-super-fast-version-of-good-riddance-time-of-your-life-as-fans-leave-for-big-lightning-storm-3784521">当粉丝们离开去参加“大闪电风暴”时，观看绿日乐队的超快版本“Good Riddance (Time Of Your Life)”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Sixpence None The Richer 原创阵容分享 20 年来第一首新歌《We Are Love》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/sixpence-none-the-richers-original-line-up-share-first-new-song-in-20-years-we-are-love-3784510？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=六便士-无富人原创阵容分享20年我们相爱第一首新歌Anagricel DuranFri, 16 Aug 2024 17:11:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3784510 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sixpence None the Richer 的 Matt Slocum、Leigh Nash 和 Justin Cary 于 2012 年 8 月 7 日在纽约参观 SiriusXM 工作室。 （辛迪·奥德/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是乐队即将发行的 EP &#39;Rosemary Hill&#39; 的主打单曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sixpence-none-the-richers-original-line-up-share-first-new-song-in-20-years-we-are-love-3784510">Sixpence None The Richer 的原创阵容分享了 20 年来的第一首新歌，《We Are Love》</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sixpence None the Richer 的 Matt Slocum、Leigh Nash 和 Justin Cary 于 2012 年 8 月 7 日在纽约参观 SiriusXM 工作室。 （辛迪·奥德/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Sixpence-none-the-richer-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Sixpence-None-The-Richer">Sixpence None The Richer</a>分享了《We Are Love》，这是该乐队 20 年来首次以原创阵容创作新歌。</p><p>这首歌是美国另类摇滚乐队新EP中的第一首歌曲，该乐队以单曲“Kiss Me”（1998年）和“Breathe Your Name”（2002年）而闻名。他们的新 EP“Rosemary Hill”将于 10 月 4 日通过 Flatiron 发行。您可以<a href="https://flatironrecordings.shop/products/sixpence-none-the-richer-rosemary-hill" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里预订</a>。</p><p> 《We Are Love》以浓烈的原声吉他搭配雷鸣般的和声和尖锐的电吉他连复段为特色，主唱 Leigh Nash 唱道： <em>“We are love, we can make it</em><br /><em>我们是你无法打破的锁链/漫长的黑暗已经到来/但仇恨在这里出现/我们是爱，我们可以接受它。”</em> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="我们是爱" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9O2Gdx1Yzck?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-vM9z0Oct3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: